## Security

- Embed-only + whitelist only; no secrets in `client-sites/`
- Do not add real PII without user approval for demo sites

## Do not

- Auto-send the **initial** quotation without a clear yes
- Ask a second cadence question after the user already said yes to send (default `3d1w` + `autoFollowUp: true` + `maxFollowUps: 4`)
- Commit `OUTREACH_SECRET` / `.outreach_secret` / `.env`
- Skip `autoFollowUp` when scheduling after a yes-to-send
- Deploy outreach.php without passing `hosting-php/tests/run-unit.php`
- Commit Netlify tokens / bypass embed-only guards
